room_title: Escape room "Detention" by Key Quest in San Jose
room_address: 1035 E Capitol Expy San Jose, CA 95121
room_description: There is a huge party at a friend's house today, but you've been sent to detention! You know the math teacher has left clues how to escape out of here to see who's been listening in class. Can you find them in 45 minutes and still make it to the party?
